extendedInfo.description: A cherry blossom is the flower of any of several trees of genus Prunus, particularly the Japanese Cherry, Prunus serrulata, which is sometimes called sakura after the Japanese. This happened for about 1 week in a Year. It is one of the best tourist Attraction for Japan. Experience the magic as a Live Wallpaper. Created in 3D with Special lighting to enhance the effect and beauty. Options for transparent box2 different light sourceOption to move lightOption to change viewing angle and change background color.Option for Auto rotation with speed control, or manual control with finger swipe.
